Intellisense shows method &quot;DoSomething&quot; as a suggestion for variables that don't match the generic type constraint of the method.

Code below, type `d.` and see &quot;DoSomething&quot; show up in the suggested list:

```
using System;

namespace broke
{
    public class SomeClass
    {
    }

    public static class SomeTypeExtensions
    {
        public static void DoSomething<TType>(this TType type) where TType : SomeClass
        {
        }
    }

    class Program
    {
        static void Main(string[] args)
        {
            IDisposable d;
        }
    }
}
```

